Theorem size_of_Number_swap:
  ∀x ys i lim refs seen n refs1 seen1.
    (size_of lim (x::Number i::ys) refs seen = (n,refs1,seen1))
    ⇔ (size_of lim (Number i::x::ys) refs seen = (n,refs1,seen1))
Proof
